WEBVTT

00:00:28.400 --> 00:00:30.816
So how are we going to do this?

00:00:30.840 --> 00:00:33.016
[Great Big Story
in partnership with TED]

00:00:33.040 --> 00:00:35.520
Narrator: They had a big idea
to change the world.

00:00:37.360 --> 00:00:39.256
But they couldn't do it alone.

00:00:39.280 --> 00:00:42.656
(Voices overlapping)
So, my wish ... My wish ... I wish ...

00:00:42.680 --> 00:00:45.376
And now, here's my wish ...

00:00:45.400 --> 00:00:47.216
[Torchbearers]

00:00:47.240 --> 00:00:49.760
[Ideas in action]

00:00:52.760 --> 00:00:54.216
SP: I am an archaeologist,

00:00:54.240 --> 00:00:59.496
and I specialize in using satellite
imagery to map ancient landscapes.

00:00:59.520 --> 00:01:02.056
The really fun title is space archaeology.